snippet.title: The Smashing Pumpkins - Bullet With Butterfly Wings | Soul/Funk AI Cover
snippet.description:
Bullet With Butterfly Wings by The Smashing Pumpkins twisted into Soul/Funk music

Like what you hear? Help keep the party going!
https://tiptopjar.com/TwistedMusicStudio

Lyrics:

The world is a vampire
Sent to drain
Secret destroyers
Hold you up to the flames
And what do I get
For my pain?
Betrayed desires
And a piece of the game

Even though I know
I suppose I'll show
All my cool and cold
Like ol' Job

Despite all my rage, I am still just a rat in a cage

Someone will say, "What is lost can never be saved"

Now I'm naked
Nothing but an animal
But can you fake it
For just one more show?
And what do you want?
I wanna change
And what do you got!
When you feel the same?

I suppose I'll show
All my cool and cold
Like ol' Job
